data.description: Welcome home to this charming bungalow full of character right in the heart of Johnson City!  You're greeted with a shaded and private front yard that leads you to a fabulous covered porch.  Come inside to a large family room, gorgeous hardwood floors and thick molding.  This updated home flows beautifully to a sunroom, and 3 nice-sized bedrooms down the wide hallway.  The renovated kitchen boasts new granite counters, new appliances and shiplap.  You'll love the spacious laundry/mudroom at the back of the house, perfect for storing your bookbags and jackets!  The basement includes a finished room, providing possibilities for an office or playroom or simply additional storage.  Off the mudroom, walk out onto a lovely deck and enjoy the fresh air!  The level, fenced yard provides the perfect space for a play yard and pets, or your favorite chicken coop! The attached double carport and paved driveway complete the property.  Located on the corner of E Chilhowie and N Broadway, you're just a couple of blocks away from the Rotary and Civitan Parks, offering playgrounds, splash pad, soccer fields and more! Schedule your private showing of this home today!
